name: Pepe CEO
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is Pepe CEO (PEO)?

Launched in 02/03/2023 by a Team based in United States of America, Pepe CEO is a decentralized meme token that rewards its holders with USDT. A decentralized application is available on the website of Pepe CEO for all the holders to track their balance in tokens, rewards, and also the total amount of rewards that was given to all the holders of PEO token. Pepe CEO token was built on Binance Smart Chain network with 10 million total supply. Currently is available for trading on PancakeSwap and P2B Centralized Exchange.
